s":["equivalent of <b>Alice</b> ."]}]}],"historicEvents":[{"id":1705197,"age":22,"year":"1455","julianDay":2252488,"title":"Wars of the Roses","description":"Wars of the Roses was a series of English civil wars for control of the throne of England between the royal families House of Lancaster and the House of York. The name of the war was derived as the red rose was the symbol of the Lancastrians and the white rose was the symbol of the Yorks.","url":"https://www.history.com/topics/british-history/wars-of-the-roses","urlTitle":"History - Wars of the Roses","jurisdictionLevel":2}],"lifeSummary":"Alice Newton was born in 1433, in Worfield, Shropshire, England. She had at least 1 son with John Rowley. She died in 1465, in her hometown, at the age of 32."},"et":{"1433–1465":"1433–1465","1428–Male":"1428–Surnud","1450–1489":"1450–1489","1489":"1489","1433":"1433","1455":"1455","1465":"1465","1450":"1450","1428":"1428","about 1450":"umbes 1450","Burslem, Staffordshire, England":"Burslem, Staffordshire, England","Worfield, Bridgnorth, Shropshire, England, United Kingdom":"Worfield, Shropshire, England"},"fi":{"1433–1465":"1433–1465","1428–Male":"1428–Kuollut","1450–1489":"1450–1489","1489":"1489","1433":"1433","1455":"1455","1465":"1465","1450":"1450","1428":"1428","about 1450":"noin 1450","Burslem, Staffordshire, England":"Burslem, Staffordshire, England","Worfield, Bridgnorth, Shropshire, England, United Kingdom":"Worfield, Shropshire, England"},"fr":{"1433–1465":"1433–1465","1428–Male":"1428–Décédé","1450–1489":"1450–1489","1489":"1489","1433":"1433","1455":"1455","1465":"1465","1450":"1450","1428":"1428","about 1450":"environ 1450","Burslem, Staffordshire, England":"Burslem, Staffordshire, Angleterre","Worfield, Bridgnorth, Shropshire, England, United Kingdom":"Worfield, Shropshire, Angleterre","lifeSummary":"Alice Newton est née en 1433, à Worfield, Shropshire, Angleterre. Elle a eu au moins 1 fils avec John Rowley. Elle est décédée en 1465, dans sa ville natale, à l’